      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must address physics and geometry representative of the intended use at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under blood-analog fluid conditions. Physics regime (turbulent rotating flow with scalar transport) matches the intended simulation use."
